title: Kull
description:
By request from the forums, This torrent contains Marvel Comics&#039; Kull the Conqueror/Destroyer v1 and Kull and the Barbarians. I have also included a couple of the original stories that pre-date the series from Creatures on the Loose #10  by Bernie Wrightson and Monsters on the Prowl by John and Marie Severin (a re-print from another book). 

This is all the Kull that I have, but I wanted to put it out there to get the ball rolling.

Thanks to the scanners and the original sources which include but are not limited to the various efforts to provide us with Marvel Chronologies.

Please seed. Please enjoy.
